      <title>巴克莱预计美联储作出关键决定前美元将上涨 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/barclays-sees-dollar-rallying-1-ahead-of-fed-s-crucial-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱外汇策略师斯凯拉·蒙哥马利·科宁表示，由于交易员高估了美联储降息的幅度，并低估了周二的零售销售报告，美元有望上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/barclays-sees-dollar-rallying-1-ahead-of-fed-s-crucial-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 19:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
