    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长哈萨克表示将进一步降息但不会降得太快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/ecb-s-kazaks-says-rates-to-be-cut-further-but-not-too-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行将进一步放松货币政策，但由于通胀风险依然存在，欧洲央行不宜过急采取这一措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/ecb-s-kazaks-says-rates-to-be-cut-further-but-not-too-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 18:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP 寻求专注于核心业务以提升投资者兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bp-seeks-to-focus-on-core-business-to-boost-investor-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司 (BP Plc) 周一宣布计划出售其在美国的陆上风电业务，因为这家石油和天然气巨头正在减少对可再生能源的投资并专注于其核心业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bp-seeks-to-focus-on-core-business-to-boost-investor-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 18:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
